svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 21, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mpe1665702721372.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mpe1665702721372.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mpe1665702721372.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mpe1665702721372\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Keep extra Japanese characters for compatibility. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__topic_d143573e1_d143574e1_d143575e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__p_d143576e1_d143577e1_d143578e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$USE_EXTRA_JIS_CHARS</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__section_sjk_zmm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d232472e67\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__ul_aml_1nm_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__li_d50222e1_d50223e1_d50224e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—use extra Japanese characters.\n               This is the default value.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__li_d50225e1_d50226e1_d50227e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—don't use extra Japanese\n               characters.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__section_i1f_bnm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d232472e86\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__table_d17084e1_d17085e1_d17086e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__section_sdy_dnm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d232472e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__p_d143588e1_d143589e1_d143590e1\">For a Japanese environment, Uniface supports\n            characters of JIS X 0208, NEC special characters, NEC selection of IBM extensions, and\n            IBM extensions (only supported on Shift-JIS). In addition, Uniface supports some extra\n            characters for compatibility reasons.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mpe1665702721372__p_d143591e1_d143592e1_d143593e1\">If you don't want to use those extra characters,\n            set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$USE_EXTRA_JIS_CHARS</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530021\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530021\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$USE_EXTRA_JIS_CHARS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 21, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Keep extra Japanese characters for compatibility. $USE_EXTRA_JIS_CHARS { = } 1 | 0 Arguments 1 —use extra Japanese characters. This is the default value. 0 —don't use extra Japanese characters. Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 1 Description For a Japanese environment, Uniface supports characters of JIS X 0208, NEC special characters, NEC selection of IBM extensions, and IBM extensions (only supported on Shift-JIS). In addition, Uniface supports some extra characters for compatibility reasons. If you don't want to use those extra characters, set $USE_EXTRA_JIS_CHARS to 0 . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}